<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 2026</p>

<p>Welcome to <strong>rentist/</strong> (“we”, “our”, “us”). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your information when you use our website and associated mobile application.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>
<p>We may collect the following type of information:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Personal information (such as name, email address, phone number if voluntarily provided)</li>
    <li>Device information (such as device type, operating system, IP address)</li>
    <li>Usage data (features used, time spent, pages viewed)</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the information for the following purposes:</p>
<ul>
    <li>To provide and maintain our services</li>
    <li>To personalize user experience</li>
    <li>To improve website and app performance</li>
    <li>To communicate updates or support messages</li>
</ul>

<h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
<p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to any third parties for marketing.</p>
<p>Your data may be shared only:</p>
<ul>
    <li>When required by law</li>
    <li>To protect our rights</li>
    <li>With analytics and service providers who support functionality</li>
</ul>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>We may use third-party analytics or hosting services that may collect information. These services have their own privacy policies.</p>

<h2>Security of Your Data</h2>
<p>We follow reasonable measures to secure your data, but no internet transmission can be 100% secure.</p>

<h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>Our services are not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect data from them.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have rights to access, update, or delete your personal information. Contact us if you wish to do this.</p>

<h2>Changes to Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted here with a revised “Last Updated” date.</p>

